 * @package   Handlebars
 * @author    fzerorubigd <fzerorubigd@gmail.com>
 * @copyright 2010-2012 (c) Justin Hileman
 * @copyright 2012 (c) ParsPooyesh Co
 * @license   MIT <http://opensource.org/licenses/MIT>
